text: Input/Output Data The Input/Output data is the type of data that an agent expects to receive and delivers. The agent expects UDRs of the type SalesForceSubscribeUDR , and it can deliver UDRs of the type SalesForceResponseUDR. See Salesforce Streaming API UDRs for further information. MIM The Salesforce Streaming API agent does not have any agent specific MIM parameters.
